Multiple award-winning Nigerian singer, Tiwa Savage has been added to the list of performers at this year’s Wireless Festival holding in London. The organisers of the Wireless Festival announced that Savage will be joining a powerful line up of artists that include the likes of Cardi B, Migos, Travis Scott, Future and ASAP Rocky. This was made known on Wednesday, March 13, 2019, as they unveiled a new set of artists that had been included to join the previously announced names. See the tweet making the announcement and her response below, Might be wrong but I think I’m the first afrobeats female to do this, no pressure but we GON kill it by HIS grace @WirelessFest @Festicket pic.twitter.com/JCk7kazn3H — Tiwa Savage (@TiwaSavage) March 13, 2019  